Your path to professional makeup mastery starts here.

Comprehensive product and tool knowledge.
In-depth understanding of different eye shapes and techniques for perfectly blended eyes using various eyeshadow shades.
Tips and tricks for working with different skin textures.

Advanced methods for concealing and correcting skin imperfections without using excessive product.

Signature looks for parties, Mehendi/Haldi, engagements/cocktails, weddings, and receptions.
Building and managing your Instagram profile, effective social media management, advertising techniques, and Instagram paid promotions.
